TypeScript has a mirror package, **`@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk`** (`npm install @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk`): the same `query()` function with async iteration, the same options, tools, and hooks:

```typescript
import { query } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

for await (const message of query({
  prompt: "Find all TODOs in the project and make a list",
  options: { allowedTools: ["Read", "Grep"], maxTurns: 10 },
})) {
  console.log(message);
}
```
